{"tid":1009381,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[豬年出嫁］［又少個處女］屋邨港姐陳庭欣 俾億萬男友確認地位 拖實返豪宅","createTime":"2019-02-05T06:43:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T03:03:55.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"0340bda965c11ab695d39bc87b988dc09a842fb6","tid":1009381,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T06:43:45.000Z","msg":"恭喜！恭喜！睇嚟踏入豬年第一單喜事，就係陳庭欣Toby同過億身家嘅彩豐行老闆Benny（楊振源）結婚喇！早前，Toby以老闆娘姿態陪實Benny 出席化妝品協會周年晚宴，雖然拍拖未夠一年，但係Benny已確認佢嘅地位。由開始拍拖到而家，Toby同Benny一直都有啲避忌，直到近日傳出佢哋會喺豬年結婚，二人終於唔介意公開放閃喇！呢日壹仔見到佢同未來老公仔Benny出街拍拖，係好高調咁拍拖，唔似以前好避忌！ 無化妝嘅Toby戴住Cap帽同benny拖到實，仲邊行邊傾，兩個幾乎全程都十指緊扣住，好sweet！見toby笑到四萬咁口，就知佢夠晒幸褔啦！佢哋會合咗兩個Friend，見Toby同個朋友傾得好開心，又拖實手，又搭膊頭。但Toby都無冷落Benny，玩咗陣就自動自覺返去拖返實男友，又再十指緊扣，真係閃到爆呀！睇完戲，佢哋就一齊返Benny天璽屋企慢慢玩啦！對於做豬年新娘，Toby就話：「大家有講過結婚呢個話題，佢有問過我結婚想點搞，但我好傳統，一定要跪地求婚先得！」跪地求婚呢個要求好easy，大家等Toby公布好消息啦！<br />\n【獲狼人Hugh Jackman探班】入行9年 陳庭欣最威唱過《大娛樂家》主題曲   <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n攝錄：陳亦龍<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_653394_0?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_653394_0%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFiIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=9e381bed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_653394_0%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=39e5ec5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_653394_0?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <