避忌！ 無化妝嘅Toby戴住Cap帽同benny拖到實，仲邊行邊傾，兩個幾乎全程都十指緊扣住，好sweet！見toby笑到四萬咁口，就知佢夠晒幸褔啦！佢哋會合咗兩個Friend，見Toby同個朋友傾得好開心，又拖實手，又搭膊頭。但Toby都無冷落Benny，玩咗陣就自動自覺返去拖返實男友，又再十指緊扣，真係閃到爆呀！睇完戲，佢哋就一齊返Benny天璽屋企慢慢玩啦！對於做豬年新娘，Toby就話：「大家有講過結婚呢個話題，佢有問過我結婚想點搞，<span style=\"color: red;\">但我好傳統，一定要跪地求婚</span>先得！」跪地求婚呢個要求好easy，大家等Toby公布好消息啦！<br />\n【獲狼人Hugh Jackman探班】入行9年 陳庭欣最威唱過《大娛樂家》主題曲   <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n攝錄：陳亦龍<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_653394_0?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_653394_0%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFiIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=9e381bed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_653394_0%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=39e5ec5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_653394_0?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢究竟知唔知乜嘢叫傳統?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7c63d76e97e66611eab8f5a3eb6560cd974b742","tid":1009381,"uid":128301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cf728a4ec0a358f2ac29ec663f976a3ed4adc1f","tid":1009381,"uid":12581,"like":